# Single-Purpose Site

This is Mirna Single-Purpose Site. It tells you whether it is weekend yet or not. If not, it shows the time left for the weekend.

Unfortunately, I wasn't able to deploy to heroku. I tried a lot!
It works fine using shotgun but when I run foreman start web(locally), it gives me errors. 
